case_circumstances: The decedent and friends were drinking the night of September 17 at one of the friends' homes between 8:00 p.m. and approximately 10:45 p.m. The friends reported that the decedent had been drinking heavily. The friends that were with him reported seeing him go into his home after leaving. In the morning, one of the friends attempted to wake the decedent and he was unresponsive. His tentative identification was given as "Candelario Talvera" or "candelario Ambrosio".
